  <entry>
    <title>LoadSystem</title>
    <link href="/2023/02/24/Onix-LoadSystem/"/>
    <url>/2023/02/24/Onix-LoadSystem/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="系统引导"><a href="#系统引导" class="headerlink" title="系统引导"></a>系统引导</h1><blockquote><p>因为这学期开始学习操作系统课程，去年短短续续写了好久的 Onix 感觉有很多的内容因为知识不足难以进行下去<br>现在开始学习操作系统希望可以重新更加深刻的来看一下这个系统的实现过程，<br>在这几天的学习过程我发现理论和实现之间的壁垒确实很难逾越，如果我们的学习永远都停留在理论的基础上<br>我相信我们很难产生一个深刻的理解和长远的进步的<br>最后：我知道这一年你可能会过的很辛苦，但是过的繁忙本身就是一种幸福！</p></blockquote><h2 id="boot-amp-amp-loader"><a href="#boot-amp-amp-loader" class="headerlink" title="boot &amp;&amp; loader"></a>boot &amp;&amp; loader</h2><h3 id="Boot"><a href="#Boot" class="headerlink" title="Boot"></a>Boot</h3><p>BIOS 在加电自检会将硬盘的主引导扇区读到 <code>0x7c00</code> 的位置，并且跳转到这里进行执行<br>boot.asm 部分长度有限，因为要实现从硬盘中加载引导程序，并且要将长度控制到 512 - 2 (这里的引导程序末尾是 <code>0x55aa</code>)</p><figure class="highlight x86asm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs x86asm"><span class="hljs-comment">; boot.asm</span><br>[org <span class="hljs-number">0x7c00</span>]<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">edi</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0x1000</span>  <span class="hljs-comment">; 目标内存</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">ecx</span>, <span class="hljs-number">2</span>       <span class="hljs-comment">; 起始扇区</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">mov</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">bl</span>, <span class="hljs-number">4</span>        <span class="hljs-comment">; 读取扇区数量</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">call</span> read_disk<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">cmp</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">word</span> [<span class="hljs-number">0x1000</span>], <span class="hljs-number">0x55aa</span>  <span class="hljs-comment">; 比较末尾的魔数</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">jnz</span> error<br><span class="hljs-keyword">jmp</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0x1002</span>               <span class="hljs-comment">; 进行 20 位内的跳转</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol"></span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">read_disk:</span> <span class="hljs-comment">; 实现硬盘的读取</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">print:</span>     <span class="hljs-comment">; 实现打印函数</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">error:</span>     <span class="hljs-comment">; 错误输出</span><br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">times</span> <span class="hljs-number">510</span> - ($ - $$) <span class="hljs-built_in">db</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>   <span class="hljs-comment">; 填充 0 ($ - $$) 计算本号距离程序开始的长度</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">db</span> <span class="hljs-number">0x55</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0xaa</span>    <span class="hljs-comment">; 结尾魔数</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
